    <h1>Highlighted Projects</h1>
    <p>I have shipped over a dozen titles on systems ranging from the Amiga and CDTV, MS-DOS, Atari Lynx, Super Nintendo, Genesis, 3DO, and PlayStation. These are some of the accomplishments I am most proud of:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ballz">Ballz</a> — the only 3D fighting game for the Super Nintendo</li>
      <li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Game_Genie">Game Genie</a> for the Super Nintendo</li>
      <li>SNES &amp; Genesis Development Systems (ISA card) — <a href="https://sourceforge.net/projects/drdevtools/">SourceForge</a>, <a href="https://www.openhub.net/p/drdevtools">OpenHub</a></li>
      <li>DRAW — custom cartridge-based Artist Workstation for Genesis &amp; Super Nintendo</li>
      <li><a href="https://worldfoundry.org/v1-levels/">World Foundry 3D Game Engine</a> and Production Pathway</li>
      <li><a href="http://russound.com/product_detail.php?i=3241">Russound SMS-3</a> Media Server</li>
      <li><a href="http://foswiki.org/">Foswiki</a> — successor to TWiki</li>
      <li><a href="/claude/">Claude Code plugins</a> — personal marketplace of techops, design, and productivity skills</li>
    </ul>
